Combine codebooks for classcodes objects

Source: R/codebook.R
codebooks.Rd

Combine codebooks for classcodes objects

codebooks(..., file = NULL)

Arguments

...

named output from codebook
file

name of Excel file for data export

Value

Concatenated list with output from codebook. Only one 'README' object is kept however and renamed as such.

See also

codebook

Examples

c1 <- codebook(elixhauser, "icd10")
#> Classification based on: regex_icd10
c2 <- codebook(elixhauser, "icd9cmd",
  cc_args = list(regex = "regex_icd9cm_enhanced")
  )
codebooks(elix_icd10 = c1, elix_icd9cm = c2)
